<doc id="1277924" wikidata="Q35341" url="?curid=1277924" title="Saint-Christophe, Aosta Valley">
<text>Saint-Christophe (; Valdôtain: ) is a town and &quot;comune&quot; in the Aosta Valley. It is located east of Aosta, on the left shore of the Dora Baltea.

== Landmarks ==
*Passerin d&#x27;Entrèves castle

==Transport==
Aosta Valley Airport is located in Saint-Christophe, in Les-Îles.

== Sport ==
*École de Football Saint-Christophe

==Twinnings==
* Bellegarde-sur-Valserine, France

==References==
==External links==

